    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>官方QQ群：1004270121</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>当星辰成为猎场，你选择沉沦欲望，还是撕裂黑暗？</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >一款融合roguelike生存射击与机甲养成的科幻动作游戏，以类&quot;吸血鬼幸存者&quot;快节奏战斗为核心，带来肾上腺素飙升的星际求生体验。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2360100/extras/370eccfd8d708ae611919120d09ed5d5.avif?t=1769489872\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2360100/extras_big/370eccfd8d708ae611919120d09ed5d5.avif?t=1769489872 width=1560 height=878 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>主角团队设定：</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在这一片混乱的星际中，一支由星际海盗和走私者组成的小队悄然降临。他们是被稀有资源的诱惑驱动的冒险者，小队成员各具特色，包括机甲专家、战斗专家和飞船专家。面对古神的威胁，他们不仅要在这片星际中生存，还要对抗古神的操控，解救被控制的美少女战斗机甲驾驶员。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2360100/extras/76e8ec2dfe9c220d220f3bcbc4f70bba.avif?t=1769489872\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2360100/extras_big/76e8ec2dfe9c220d220f3bcbc4f70bba.avif?t=1769489872 width=1560 height=878 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>玩法亮点：</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >永夜中的生存博弈：在神秘星系废墟中，操控战争机甲，迎战潮水般的畸变生物；</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2360100/extras/af6911cf1393d1ebf73aea8ce5371ab6.avif?t=1769489872\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2360100/extras_big/af6911cf1393d1ebf73aea8ce5371ab6.avif?t=1769489872 width=1560 height=878 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >堕落与救赎的永恒抉择：解救被精神控制的机甲少女，通过「神经同步」解锁合体必杀技；</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >深空基地建设：收集资源，升级母舰科技树，解锁机甲隐形力场/驾驶员基因改造仓；</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >16 种基础武器 + 27 种高阶合成武器，每款自带近 10 种形态强化分支，再搭配上百种被动技能自由组合！Build 套路无上限，尽情发挥脑洞，打造专属于你的无敌战斗流派！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >机甲、技能与武器：根据自己的战斗风格选择不同的机甲、武器，是激活能量护盾稳扎稳打，还是堆叠暴走模组化身战场绞肉机？你的战术DNA将定义整个星系的毁灭形态！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >视觉冲击：见证机械与生物组织融合的畸变体，在动态光影下呈现另类恐怖；</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2360100/extras/621920c144e481c6c381277c1f0d68e3.avif?t=1769489872\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2360100/extras_big/621920c144e481c6c381277c1f0d68e3.avif?t=1769489872 width=1560 height=878 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2360100/extras/6fae71ab549174844d6384ff93ea1b33.avif?t=1769489872\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2360100/extras_big/6fae71ab549174844d6384ff93ea1b33.avif?t=1769489872 width=1560 height=864 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>加入这场银河级豪赌——在疯狂与理智的边缘，改写文明存续的最终方程式！</strong></p>",
